  <front>
   <head>Stella and Flavia.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">and , ev'ry Hour,</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Unnumber'd Hearts surprize:</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">In  Soul lies all her Pow'r,</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">And , in her Eyes.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="2" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="5" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">More boundless  Conquests are,</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">And  more confin'd:</l>
     <l n="7" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">All can discern a Face that's fair,</l>
     <l n="8" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">But few a lovely Mind.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="3" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="9" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">, like  Monarch, reigns</l>
     <l n="10" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">O'er cultivated Lands;</l>
     <l n="11" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Like  Tyrants,  deigns</l>
     <l n="12" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">To rule o'er barren Sands.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="4" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="13" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Then boast, fair , boast your Face,</l>
     <l n="14" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Your Beauty's only Store:</l>
     <l n="15" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Your Charms will ev'ry Day decrease,</l>
     <l n="16" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Each Day gives  more.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
